### Login owner
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "andrey@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Create company
POST http://localhost:3000/api/companies
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "StayFlow Marbella"
}

### Create company-scoped property
POST http://localhost:3000/api/properties
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Apartment Marbella 01",
  "address": "Marbella Center",
  "city": "Marbella"
}

### List only my properties
GET http://localhost:3000/api/properties
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN

### Create booking only for my property
POST http://localhost:3000/api/bookings
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "propertyId": "PASTE_PROPERTY_ID",
  "guestName": "John Smith",
  "checkInDate": "2026-08-01",
  "checkOutDate": "2026-08-05"
}
